reviewText:
Love this Anime.  Yes some of the movements of the characters are a bit jerky, but the story is so good!  Can't wait for next season!!
The DVD came undamaged and on time.
Saw this on Netflix. Is this DVD box set in English?
Love this show - the rating is not G, though, it's MA. Very MA. I didn't want anybody to think this was a kids show or anything because that's what it says in the current product description
